<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.2.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-hWVjflwFxL6sNzntih27bfxkr27PmbbK/iSvJ+a4+0owXq79v+lsFkW54bOGbiDQ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,700" rel="stylesheet"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html,
        body {
            margin: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Open Sans';
        }

        .splash-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #FF9100;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .splash-container .title {
            
            color: white;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

            .splash-container .links {
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                right: 0;
                padding: 10px;
                border-radius: 0 0 0 4px;
                background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
          
            }

            .splash-container .links ul {
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                display: block;
                list-style: none;
            }

                .splash-container .links li {
                    display: inline;
                    font-size: 20px;
                    margin-right: 5px;
                }
              
                .splash-container .links a {
                    text-decoration: none;
                    color: white;
                }
        #me {
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px grey;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background-color: red;
            border-radius: 100%;
            border: none;
            border: 4px solid white;
        }

        .splash-info {
            text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .more {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, 0);
       

        }

            .more a {
                width: 200px;
                background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
                padding: 10px;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                transition: 0.3s;
            }

        .more a:hover {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .content-container {
            min-height: 600px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

    

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="splash-container">
        <div class="splash-info">
            <img id="me" src="~/img/myAvatar.png" />
            <h1 class="title">Emilio Kyprianidis</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="more">
            <a onclick="scroll">Check out more</a>
        </div>
        <div class="links">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="facebook.com"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i></a></li>
                <li><a href="instagram.com"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a></li>
                <li><a href="github.com"<i class="fab fa-github-square"></i></a></li>
                <li><a href="linkedin.com"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="content" class="content-container">
        <h1>Hello World!</h1>
        <hr />
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque facilisis augue sit amet sem porta auctor. Nam posuere semper metus, vitae egestas nibh tempus sit amet. Vestibulum non pharetra nisi. Praesent quis elit tempus, fermentum velit eget, condimentum purus. Nulla</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>